@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC011 JoinFamilyGroup

actor "User" as Actor
boundary "JoinGroupUI" as UI
control "JoinGroupController" as Controller
entity "FamilyDB" as Entity

Actor -> UI : 1. Nhập mã mời / Click link
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. joinGroup(inviteCode)
activate Controller
Controller -> Entity : 3. validateToken(inviteCode)
activate Entity
Entity --> Controller : 4. tokenValid (groupId)
deactivate Entity
Controller -> Entity : 5. addMemberToGroup(userId, groupId)
activate Entity
Entity --> Controller : 6. success
deactivate Entity
Controller --> UI : 7. Thông báo tham gia thành công
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 8. Hiển thị trang nhóm gia đình mới tham gia
deactivate UI
@enduml
